# Xrefs

Type-aware reverse lookup of a Go symbol. Use before renaming a
function or changing a signature.

1. Ask the user for the symbol (bare name, `pkg.Func`, or
   `pkg.Type.Method`).
2. Run `gofasta xrefs <Symbol> --json`.
3. Report the definition location and every reference site (file,
   line, enclosing function).
4. If the result is `AMBIGUOUS_SYMBOL`, ask the user which package
   they meant and re-run with the fully-qualified form.
